\begin_layout Section
Lathe Mode
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When you set up a lathe using Lathe Mode you need to use a Lathe Tool Table
 so AXIS will display your tool properly.
 See the INI File section of the Integrators Manual for info on setting
 up AXIS for Lathe Mode.
 Use the "DIA" column for the tool tip diameter.
